<plot>A contemporary twist on a Shakespearean tragedy with a nod to French New Wave cinema, this short film focuses on the rapid decline of a seemingly perfect marriage. After returning from a long business trip, the brooding Theo savors his reconnection with Mona, his loving and beautiful wife. However, when he observes an apparent series of "chance" encounters between Mona and his best friend, Michael, Theo becomes haunted by images of an illicit affair. Theo's jealousy and obsessive fantasies increasingly obscure reality and truth, leading to a tragic conclusion.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?375226</url></doc>
